    "Both the PacBio and ONT datasets showed the same coordinates for the variant, and no read support was found in the control.",
    "https://doi.org/10.1038/s41587-023-02024-y events, as the VCF standard does not provide a clear recommendation.",
    "Currently, these complex alleles would need to be reported as independent breakend (BND) events, which lose their individual impact (for example, DUP-TRP/INV-DUP and DUP-NML-INV/DUP) on the region itself.",
    "Nevertheless, this is clearly needed, as our experiments on the Mendelian cohort show.",
    "Overall, we report here the innovations across Sniffles2 and highlight them across Mendelian cases, a patient with MSA and a tumor/ normal comparison."
